        <p class="padding heading" id="feature1"><strong>Campaign Management</strong>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Offer Access Control</strong>:- Control which affiliate have access to your offers by settings access status to Public, Required Approval or Private.</li>
          <li><strong>Smart Links & Groups</strong>:- Group your offers and generate one tracking link which will act as an AI powered smart link.</li>
          <li><strong>Multiple Landing URLs</strong>:- For a single campaign, you can have multiple landing page URLs and you can redirect traffic to different landing URLs by defining targeting rules such as country or device.</li>
          <li><strong>Block Affiliates/ Sub-Affiliates</strong>:- Sometimes you may want to block all the traffic getting to a specific offer from some affiliates who send fraudulent or low quality traffic. In that case, you can use block affiliate/sub affiliates feature to block those.</li>
          <li><strong>Offer Caps Management</strong>:- Apply specific caps to your offers by the amount conversions, revenue or payout by daily, monthly or total basis. You can also define specific caps by affiliate as well.</li>
          <li><strong>Offer Creatives</strong>:- Upload,share and manage offer creatives. Let your affiliates upload creatives for your approval.</li>
          <li><strong>Dynamic Payouts</strong>:- Pay different payout/revenue amounts for a single offer by using advanced payout groups. You can setup different payout amounts by country, device, affiliate, sub affiliate.</li>
          <li><strong>Offer Events</strong>:- Have multiple events for a single offer and payouts according to that. Such as for installation event, registration event, etc.</li>
          <li><strong>Multiple Payout Models</strong>:- We support CPA, CPI, CPL, CPS & CPC payout models. We also support offers with dynamic payout/revenue amounts.</li>
          <li><strong>Live Stats Monitor</strong>:- With OffersHub real-time dashboard, you can monitor all the system events (clicks, conversions) with live charts. You can also monitor live stats by specific offer or affiliate.</li>
          <li><strong>Advanced Targeting & Traffic Filtering</strong>:- More than 20 options to define your offer targeting such as country, mobile network, os, device type, gender basis etc and OffersHub will filter traffic according to that and you will not charge for blocked traffic.</li>
        </ul>
        </p>
        <p class="padding heading" id="feature2"><strong>Fraud Control & Alerting</strong>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Built in Fraud Protection</strong>:- OffersHubs built in fraud detection system continuously monitors each of your conversions for frauds and reports it back to you while blocking conversions with higher risks</li>
          <li><strong>Alert & Notifications</strong>:- We provide real-time web and email notifications for each offer changes, team actions and fraud detections.</li>
          <li><strong>3rd Party Fraud Detector Support</strong>:- We support to connect your system with 3rd party fraud detecting systems.</li>
          <li><strong>Postback Security</strong>:- IP white-listing and advertiser security code features keeps your network away from fraud postbacks.</li>
          <li><strong>Block Bots & Fraud Traffic</strong>:- OffersHubs AI continuously watches & learns about your traffic behaviors and blocks all the bots and fraud traffic.</li>
        </ul>
        </p>
