          <li><strong>Custom Payout & Caps</strong>:- You can setup specific offer caps and payouts by affiliate.</li>
          <li><strong>Alerting & Notifications</strong>:- System will alert your affiliate about any changes about offers, so you don’t have to do it manually.</li>
          <li><strong>Affiliate API</strong>:- Affiliates can connect their system with yours using OffersHub publisher API.</li>
          <li><strong>Referral Commissions</strong>:- You can reward your affiliates for referrals with referral commission system that we provide.</li>
          <li><strong>Affiliate Billing</strong>:- OffersHub offers a total billing & invoicing solution for affiliates.</li>
